name: Sate Favorit Suzzanna
description:
A tribute to Suzzanna, an Indonesian actress who was dubbed the “Horror Queen of Indonesian Cinema” during the 1970s-1980s.

Pictured here is one of her most iconic roles: Sundel Bolong, a hungry ghost who ordered 200 pieces of Sate Ayam (Chicken Skewers), posing as a model for a local Sate Ayam stall’s advertisement.

1417 x 1811 px
200 dpi
